fields.description: Seen during testing of SPARK-1537; an NPE in the timeline server during {{AppInfo}} construction. Presumably an incomplete record passed in is the cause.
fields.summary: NPE in ATS v1 web service: AppInfo  constructor

comments.body:

curl -i -k -s   -H 'Content-Type: application/json'  -H 'Accept: application/json'    --negotiate -u : 'http://ats1:8188/ws/v1/applicationhistory/apps'
{code}
